# Windsurf Rules (IEEPIS)

Session protocol lives in `AGENTS.md`. Read it first.

Then follow the protocol:
1. `.ai/handoff.md` (always)
2. `.ai/memory.md` index (top 20 lines) → load relevant section
3. For Laravel/Filament code: `.ai/laravel-boost.md` (project-specific framework rules)
4. Optional role: `.agents/<role>.md`

Confirm loaded, then await task.
